o I cancel or change my order?','','publish','open','closed','','how-do-i-cancel-or-change-my-order','','','2026-04-22 14:53:50','2026-04-22 14:53:50','',0,'http://localhost:8080/hazara/?betterdocs_faq=how-do-i-cancel-or-change-my-order',0,'betterdocs_faq','',0),(26,1,'2026-04-22 14:53:50','2026-04-22 14:53:50','We usually take 3-5 business days for your order to be shipped & delivered.','How long does the delivery take?','','publish','open','closed','','how-long-does-the-delivery-take','','','2026-04-22 14:53:50','2026-04-22 14:53:50','',0,'http://localhost:8080/hazara/?betterdocs_faq=how-long-does-the-delivery-take',0,'betterdocs_faq','',0),(27,1,'2026-04-22 14:53:50','2026-04-22 14:53:50','Yes, free shipping is available for all the orders that\'s placed inside the United States. We charge shipping fees for overseas orders.','Do you offer free shipping?','','publish','open','closed','','do-you-offer-free-shipping','','','2026-04-22 14:53:50','2026-04-22 14:53:50','',0,'http://localhost:8080/hazara/?betterdocs_faq=do-you-offer-free-shipping',0,'betterdocs_faq','',0),(28,1,'2026-04-22 14:53:50','2026-04-22 14:53:50','Yes, we ship all over the world. Please note that additional shipping costs will be applied based on your delivery location.','Do you ship overseas?','','publish','open','closed','','do-you-ship-overseas','','','2026-04-22 14:53:50','2026-04-22 14:53:50','',0,'http://localhost:8080/hazara/?betterdocs_faq=do-you-ship-overseas',0,'betterdocs_faq','',0),(29,1,'2026-04-22 14:53:50','2026-04-22 14:53:50','You can ask for a refund within 30 days of your purchase. Returned items must be in the exact same condition as they were received.','What is your Refund & Exchange Policy?','','publish','open','closed','','what-is-your-refund-exchange-policy','','','2026-04-22 14:53:50','2026-04-22 14:53:50','',0,'http://localhost:8080/hazara/?betterdocs_faq=what-is-your-refund-exchange-policy',0,'betterdocs_faq','',0),(30,1,'2026-04-22 14:53:50','2026-04-22 14:53:50','To track the status of your refund, kindly refer to your confirmation email that you have received from us.','How do I track my Refund?','','publish','open','closed','','how-do-i-track-my-refund','','','2026-04-22 14:53:50','2026-04-22 14:53:50','',0,'http://localhost:8080/hazara/?betterdocs_faq=how-do-i-track-my-refund',0,'betterdocs_faq','',0),(31,1,'2026-04-22 14:53:50','2026-04-22 14:53:50','Once we receive your return, please allow us 3-5 business days for your refund to process. Refund amount will be automatically debited to the same form of payment originally used for purchase.','How long does it take to get the Refund?','','publish','open','closed','','how-long-does-it-take-to-get-the-refund','','','2026-04-22 14:53:50','2026-04-22 14:53:50','',0,'http://localhost:8080/hazara/?betterdocs_faq=how-long-does-it-take-to-get-the-refund',0,'betterdocs_faq','',0),(32,1,'2026-04-22 14:55:26','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\n    \"hello-elementor::betterdocs_docs_page_docs_list_item_margin_layout_8\": {\n        \"value\": \"{\\\"input1\\\":\\\"24\\\",\\\"input2\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"input3\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"input4\\\":\\\"0\\\"}\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2026-04-22 14:55:26\"\n    },\n    \"hello-elementor::betterdocs_sidebar_title_margin_layout_8\": {\n        \"value\": \"{\\\"input1\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"input2\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"input3\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"input4\\\":\\\"0\\\"}\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2026-04-22 14:55:26\"\n    },\n    \"hello-elementor::betterdocs_sidebar_title_padding_layout_8\": {\n        \"value\": \"{\\\"input1\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"input2\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"input3\\\":\\\"0\\\",\\\"input4\\\":\\\"0\\\"}\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2026-04-22 14:55:26\"\n    },\n    \"hello-elementor::betterdocs_sidebar_list_item_margin_layout_8\": {\n        \"value\": \"{\\